@startuml State_Subscription_Recommendation
title Subscription Recommendation State Machine

skinparam state {
    BackgroundColor<<initial>> LightBlue
    BackgroundColor<<analyzed>> LightYellow
    BackgroundColor<<pending>> Wheat
    BackgroundColor<<progress>> LightGreen
    BackgroundColor<<done>> LightGray
}

[*] --> Unanalyzed <<initial>> : Subscription\ndiscovered

Unanalyzed --> Analyzed <<analyzed>> : Usage analysis and\nvalue scoring complete

Analyzed --> ActionPending <<pending>> : Waste flag created with\nrecommended action
Analyzed --> Unanalyzed <<initial>> : Re-analysis triggered\nby new transactions

ActionPending --> ActionInProgress <<progress>> : User approves action\nor autonomy gate passes
ActionPending --> Analyzed <<analyzed>> : User dismisses\nrecommendation
ActionPending --> ActionPending : Recommendation\nupdated by re-analysis

ActionInProgress --> Resolved <<done>> : Action completed\nsuccessfully
ActionInProgress --> ActionPending <<pending>> : Action failed,\nawait retry decision
ActionInProgress --> Analyzed <<analyzed>> : User cancels\nin-progress action

Resolved --> Unanalyzed <<initial>> : Subscription reactivated\nor new charges detected
Resolved --> [*] : Subscription cancelled\nand confirmed

note right of Unanalyzed
  New subscription detected
  by Feature 01. Awaiting
  first analysis pass.
end note

note right of Analyzed
  Value score and usage
  profile computed. No waste
  flag if score is high.
end note

note right of ActionPending
  Waste detected. Recommendation
  (cancel, negotiate, downgrade)
  awaits user approval or
  autonomy gate clearance.
end note

note right of ActionInProgress
  Cancellation, negotiation,
  or downgrade is being
  executed by Features 03-05.
end note

note right of Resolved
  Action completed. Savings
  tracked. Subscription may
  re-enter cycle if charges
  reappear.
end note

@enduml
